Output docs/assets/library-demo.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 760
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Env PCCLI_MOCK "true"
Env PCCLI_COLOR "always"

Type "pccli"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "pccli services --help"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "pccli services songs list"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "pccli services songs arrangements 1001"
Enter
Sleep 3s
